flowchart TD
    A[Input: User Preferences + K] --> B[Load songs from CSV]
    B --> C[For each song in catalog]
    C --> D[Compute genre/mood match]
    D --> E[Compute energy closeness]
    E --> F{Tempo preference provided?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Compute tempo closeness]
    F -- No --> H[Skip tempo component]
    G --> I[Compute weighted final score]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Store song + score]
    J --> K{More songs?}
    K -- Yes --> C
    K -- No --> L[Sort by score descending]
    L --> M[Output: Top K recommendations]
